## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **immunosuppression life-long** — 모든 transplant 의 standard, 단 nephrotoxicity (calcineurin) / cardiovascular / cancer / infection risk. quantum-VQE 의 selectivity 향상 path.
2. **tolerance induction 거의 achievable 안됨** — research level, 단 experimental protocols (iCasp9 suicide gene + 등). quantum 직접 X.
3. **xenotransplantation paradigm shift** — 2022-2024 first human pig kidney / heart transplants (eGenesis CRISPR-edited). VIROCAPSID/RIBOZYME 의 gene editing 측 evidence.
4. **GvHD ruxolitinib 2019** = first FDA steroid-refractory acute GvHD; cross-link autoimmune JAK path.
5. **HLA matching computational challenge** — protein-protein interface (large-protein), VQE scope 밖. immunology / bioinformatics 영역.
6. **xenotransplant immunology** = α-Gal / Neu5Gc / Sda epitope removal (gene KO 으로 해결). quantum 직접 X, gene-edit (RIBOZYME / VIROCAPSID) 측.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, transplant 임상 의미 한정.

